data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: This picture shows a woman lying on the grass. It can be seen that the woman has very long and curly hair. The hair spreads out on the grass. Other than the grass, there are some white flowers growing out of the grass. The picture seems to be a portrait of this woman who might be a celebrity. This is a beautiful picture that reminds me of the relationship between humans and nature. I would love to lie on the grass one day only to feel nature and appreciate the world.
